The battery installation shall comply with AS 3011.1 and AS 4086.2.
The battery installation shall be in a location that isâ€”
(a)	well ventilated;
(b)	protected from direct sunlight;
(c)	protected from rain;
(d)	protected from flooding;
(e)	protected from dust;
(f)	protected from vermin;
(g)	protected from mechanical damage;
(h)	protected from corrosive atmospheres;
(i)	accessible for maintenance;
(j)	secure from unauthorized access.
